KeyBindings
public static enum KeyBindings.KEY_BIND
extends java.lang.Enum<KeyBindings.KEY_BIND>

KEY_BIND models all the different keyboard bindings for all the different actions.

Enum Constant Summary

          The keyboard key that moves the selected card down

          The keyboard key that removes the card at inlay position 2 assuming that there is a card there
RIGHT

SELECT
          The keyboard key that chooses the selected card
THREE_MORE
          The keyboard key that is binded to the 3 More Button
UNPAUSE
          The keyboard key that unpauses the game; it is the same key as pause
UP
